                <p>
                    The project we propose is a small-scale borrowing management system. In this project, users will be able to create a requirement form of borrow that serves as a license to borrow items. It creates a borrowing form where items that you borrowed are listed and you can list all the items you would like to borrow. It also includes other borrowing details such as name and age, date and purpose of borrowing items.
                </p>
